    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>shredded spring greens</strong> and <strong>chopped pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
