          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg is starting to soften, drain, then add your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
