      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your<strong> chilli relish</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> rice vinegar</strong> and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in a small bowl – this is your<strong> stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
