      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's fragrant, add the <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further, giving it a good mix up until everything is coated in the sauce and the prawns are cooked through – these are your<strong> ginger & chilli king prawns</strong></p>",
